{"data": [{"id": "4747476", "title": "ACVF: Why I'm Downgrading This Right-Leaning Conservative Values ETF", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Trump sign\" data-id=\"536863862\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1017px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">SteveChristensen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>The following article is a follow-up to my <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4718410-acvf-high-quality-etf-designed-for-conservative-values-investors\">September 1, 2024, review</a> of the <b>American Conservative Values ETF</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ACVF\" title=\"American Conservative Values ETF\">ACVF</a></span>), a four-year-old actively managed fund with $115 million in assets under management. Previously, I cautioned that ACVF's</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747476-acvf-why-downgrading-this-right-leaning-conservative-values-etf", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 17:47:13", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747486", "title": "New Record High For U.S. October Oil Production", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oil pump, oil industry equipment\" data-id=\"1327982065\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1138px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">bjdlzx</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>A guest post by Ovi</em></p> <p>All of the Crude plus Condensate (C + C) production data, oil, for the US state charts comes from the EIA\u02bcs Petroleum Supply monthly <a href=\"https://www.eia.gov/dnav/pet/pet_crd_crpdn_adc_mbblpd_m.htm\" rel=\"noopener\">PSM</a> which provides updated information up to October 2024.</p> <p></p> <p>U.S. October</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747486-new-record-high-us-october-oil-production", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 17:40:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747473", "title": "QTUM: Investing In Quantum The Right Way", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1453664340/image_1453664340.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A futuristic glowing quantum computer unit, 3d render\" data-id=\"1453664340\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1453664340/image_1453664340.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1453664340/image_1453664340.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1453664340/image_1453664340.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1453664340/image_1453664340.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1453664340/image_1453664340.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1453664340/image_1453664340.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1453664340/image_1453664340.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1453664340/image_1453664340.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">bpawesome</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis Summary</h2> <p>As Quantum Computing stocks begin to take off, investors are looking at ways to gain exposure to the industry.</p> <p>Many quantum stocks have doubled or even tripled in the last month, but these stocks are highly volatile.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1453664340/image_1453664340.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747473-qtum-investing-in-quantum-the-right-way", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 17:35:06", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747392", "title": "BCAT: Big Yield, 8% Discount On Fixed Income/Equity Mix", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/107072653/image_107072653.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Portrait of cat hissing\" data-id=\"107072653\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/107072653/image_107072653.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/107072653/image_107072653.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/107072653/image_107072653.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/107072653/image_107072653.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/107072653/image_107072653.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/107072653/image_107072653.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/107072653/image_107072653.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/107072653/image_107072653.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Flashpop</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Looking for a high-yield income vehicle with a mix of equity and fixed income? While market pundits had thought that the Fed would embark on a heavy regime of lower rates in 2024, that didn't turn out to be the case, with just</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/107072653/image_107072653.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747392-bcat-big-yield-discount-on-fixed-income-equity-mix", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 17:15:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747467", "title": "EWJ: Good Valuation And Long-Term Outlook With Significant Short-Term Risks In Mind", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824344345/image_1824344345.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Fuji mountain and Kawaguchiko lake at sunrise, Autumn seasons Fuji mountain at yamanachi in Japan.\" data-id=\"1824344345\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824344345/image_1824344345.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824344345/image_1824344345.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824344345/image_1824344345.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824344345/image_1824344345.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824344345/image_1824344345.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824344345/image_1824344345.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824344345/image_1824344345.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824344345/image_1824344345.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">tawatchaiprakobkit</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Thesis: Hold EWJ</strong></h2> <p><span>iShares MSCI Japan ETF (</span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EWJ\" title=\"iShares MSCI Japan ETF\">EWJ</a></span><span>) presents opportunities from the optimism surrounding Japan's stock market and the potential shift of its macroeconomic growth trajectory. Valuations for domestic equities and growth capacity concerning the sheer amount of corporate spare</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824344345/image_1824344345.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747467-ewj-good-valuation-and-long-term-outlook-with-significant-short-term-risks-in-mind", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 16:33:32", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747001", "title": "Buy The Dip 2: Dividend Stocks Getting Way Too Cheap", "description": "<p></p> <figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"phrase buy the dip handwritten on night wet window glass surface\" data-id=\"1289941019\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5472px\" height=\"3648px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">z1b</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p></p> <p>Dividend stocks (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SCHD\" title=\"Schwab Strategic Trust - Schwab U.S. Dividend Equity ETF\">SCHD</a>) recently suffered a dip.</p> <p>Utilities (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XLU\" title=\"Utilities Select Sector SPDR\u00ae Fund ETF\">XLU</a>), MLPs (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MLPA\" title=\"Global X MLP ETF\">MLPA</a>), REITs (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VNQ\" title=\"Vanguard Real Estate ETF\">VNQ</a>), BDCs (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BIZD\" title=\"VanEck Vectors BDC Income ETF\">BIZD</a>) etc. all dropped after the Fed revised its guidance for rate cuts in 2025.</p> <p>They still expect to cut interest rates, but they explained that they</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747001-buy-the-dip-2-dividend-stocks-getting-way-too-cheap", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 16:25:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747464", "title": "DFI Retail's Sales Make The Stock A Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Cropped image of woman with shopping bags using a mobile phone\" data-id=\"836709534\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">RUNSTUDIO</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I like <strong>DFI Retail Group Holdings'</strong> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DFILF\" title=\"DFI Retail Group Holdings Limited\">OTCPK:DFILF</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DFIHY\" title=\"DFI Retail Group Holdings Limited\">OTCPK:DFIHY</a>) (D01:SP) latest asset divestitures to retain a Buy rating for the name. Earlier, my <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4706246-dfi-retail-a-beneficiary-of-health-and-convenience-trends-rating-upgrade\">July 24, 2024, article</a> touched on the favorable growth outlook for DFILF's \"convenience</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747464-dfi-retail-sales-make-stock-buy", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 16:17:35", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747463", "title": "Funko: Easy Money Has Been Made; Time To Downgrade", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Row of figures of American company Funko Pop in the shop window\" data-id=\"961973282\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1082px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/ima